Source: shellfacts
Section: admin
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Denis "jawa" Pompilio <denis.pompilio@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://github.com/outini/shellfacts
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/outini/shellfacts.git

Package: shellfacts
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gawk
Description: Shell scripts to retrieve facts from operating systems.
 Set of various shell scripts for retrieving facts from operating systems.
 Exemple of retrieved informations:
   - network configuration and routing informations
   - system informations and sysctl configuration
   - xen hypervisor state and domUs states
   - hardware configuration
   - APT packages status
